00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:23,220
Monica was sitting in the living 
room of Owen's Hat, waiting for him.  

413
00:39:24,120 --> 00:39:27,540
He had gone to use a neighbour's 
telephone because his was out of order.  

414
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:34,440
She found a book on the table next to her. 
It was a library book on ancient Egypt.  

415
00:39:35,640 --> 00:39:39,120
She opened it to the story 
of Osiris and began to read:

