00:39:55,560 --> 00:40:02,880
it from her. He cut the body into sixteen 
separate pieces and hid them all over Egypt.  

420
00:40:03,720 --> 00:40:11,940
Again, Isis went to look for them. This time, she 
took her sister, Nephthys, with her. Together they  

