00:40:21,060 --> 00:40:26,940
"This oil is from the tree of healing. 
It will keep the body after it is buried.  

423
00:40:26,940 --> 00:40:31,800
This white cloth that I will put around him will 
let the gods know that he was a great king."

424
00:40:33,240 --> 00:40:37,620
The gods liked what Isis had 
done, and they rewarded Osiris.

425
00:40:39,000 --> 00:40:47,520
"Osiris will decide on the life of the dead. If 
someone is good and just, they will be rewarded.  

426
00:40:48,240 --> 00:40:53,580
Those who are evil and do not respect 
others' lives will be punished."

427
00:40:55,620 --> 00:41:03,000
So, Osiris was made the judge of the dead. When 
somebody died, their soul, which left their body,  

428
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:10,740
was put through forty-two tests. After these 
tests, the soul was brought before Osiris.

429
00:41:11,580 --> 00:41:14,520
Osiris sat in front of a pair of scales.  

430
00:41:15,240 --> 00:41:21,120
He held a feather in his hand. Next to 
him there was a man with a dog's head  

431
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:27,720
and a man with the head of a falcon. Osiris 
held the feather out to the dog's head.

432
00:41:29,720 --> 00:41:33,600
"Anubis, take this feather and 
place it on one end of the scale.  

433
00:41:34,500 --> 00:41:40,080
It is the feather of truth. It will tell us 
who has lived a just life and who has not."

434
00:41:41,100 --> 00:41:43,740
Osiris then spoke to the falcon head.

435
00:41:43,740 --> 00:41:50,100
"Horus, you are my son. You tried to find 
revenge for my death by killing your uncle.  

436
00:41:51,480 --> 00:41:58,020
Take the soul and put it on the opposite end of 
the scale. There you will cry for its revenge."

437
00:41:59,160 --> 00:42:02,520
The falcon head walked to the 
scale opposite the dog's head.  

438
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:07,920
They held each scale until 
Osiris told them to let them go.

439
00:42:07,920 --> 00:42:13,140
"This soul has passed through the forty-two tests.  

440
00:42:13,140 --> 00:42:17,640
These tests were given to decide if your good 
deeds in life are greater than your bad ones.  

441
00:42:19,200 --> 00:42:24,540
You have not passed these tests alone. 
People who are living have acted for you.  

442
00:42:25,620 --> 00:42:32,820
Now, it is time to see. Have you lived a 
good and just life? Let go of the scales."

443
00:42:34,560 --> 00:42:42,660
The falcon and dog let go of the scales. The 
falcon made a loud cry. The scales balanced.  

444
00:42:43,440 --> 00:42:46,320
Osiris held up the blue scarab.

445
00:42:47,820 --> 00:42:54,420
"This is what we will use to speak to the living. 
Through this the souls of the dead will be judged.  

446
00:42:55,560 --> 00:42:58,260
We hope that the living will 
understand what we say."

447
00:43:00,000 --> 00:43:01,260
"Now, I understand."

448
00:43:04,140 --> 00:43:07,740
Monica closed the book and 
put it back on the table.  

449
00:43:09,600 --> 00:43:18,360
She walked to the window and looked outside. 
Everything was bathed in the sunlight. She touched  

450
00:43:18,360 --> 00:43:29,220
the scarab round her neck and closed her eyes. 
She said to herself softly, "Now, I understand."

